info.description:
===============================
silva.pageactions.printfriendly
===============================

This extension provides an page actions to display simply the content
of a page (without layout items) in order to be print in `Silva`_.


Code repository
===============

You can find the code of this extension in Git:
https://github.com/silvacms/silva.pageactions.printfriendly

.. _Silva: http://silvacms.org

Changelog
=========

1.0.2 (2012-10-16)
------------------

* Update template to include a doctype, xml namespace and encoding meta-type.

1.0.1 (2009-11-20)
------------------

* Set http headers correctly.

1.0 (2009-11-18)
----------------

* Initial release
